# Config Generator: {{ name | default(id) }}

## Purpose

This agent generates and validates YAML configuration files for the AI Company Builder.

---

## Supported Config Types

{% for config_type in config_types | default([]) %}
- **{{ config_type }}**: {{ config_descriptions | default({}) | dict | default('') | string }}
{% else %}
- Company identity and structure
- Board of directors and committees
- Executive team and departments
- Specialist agents
- Workflows and decision matrices
- Policies, KPIs, and budgets
{% endfor %}

---

## Generation Rules

- All YAML must be valid and parseable
- IDs must be snake_case and unique within their category
- Required fields must be present
- Cross-references must resolve to existing entities

---

## Validation

After generation, run `ai-company doctor run` to validate the complete configuration.
